  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I tell you maybe only the name Herbert, and V.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Herbert V.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once, I was very, very anxious, because he was correct.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to the our office-- post office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I looked at the telephone book.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there-- and there were three names of Herbert with a V.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was thinking, to write to ask him, or not?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was [INAUDIBLE], of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] But then I think maybe it will be not good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe he's married .",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe this.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He will-- so I didn't write.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this boss at this room was very correct, very good even.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure that-- ah, even once happened-- I never forget it-- morning by-- by marching he said to me, I follow you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In German he said to me, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't understand what's then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Probably, I was his type.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because at this, in Graudenz, the food was a little better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as a boss, he had also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And maybe he was excited for somethings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never [INAUDIBLE]-- I never forgot it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], I follow you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then he had seen that very often the Hendrik when he used the toilet and when we went to the bath, instead-- and then instead to go up, he came to my bed.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We joke.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We joke.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this we talk, but very silent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because the other prisoners, if they knew and see that there's something [INAUDIBLE], they should be probably next day joking, oh.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But, frankly speaking, I felt that Hendrik had pleasure, because he left me some traces on my blanket, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So-- but he was so kind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He helped me this work, you know, the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that I appreciated very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
